dct_title_s: Sketch showing the progress of the survey on the Atlantic Gulf of Mexico and Pacific coast of the United States
dct_description_sm: "To November 1860." "No. 37." "Electrotype copy no. 3 by G. Mathiot U.S.C.S." Includes: Sub sketch showing the progress on the Pacific Coast of the United States to Nov. 1860. Historic Maps copy has extensive ms. annotations showing "Mr. Fields proposed plan for bringing Washington in telegraphic communication with Fortress Monroe ... .
